definition.value: A member of the class of quinazolines that is quinazoline which is substituted by a 4-methylphenyl group and a bis(2-methoxyethyl)nitrilo group at positions 2 and 4, respectively.
A member of the class of quinazolines that is quinazoline which is substituted by a (3-methoxyphenyl)nitrilo group at position 4.
